'''Orbot'''為一[[自由软件|自由软件]]計劃，以提供在[[互联网|互联网]]上[[Android|谷歌Android]][[智能手机|智能手机]]的[[隐私权|匿名]]應用。它作為像[[Tor|Tor]]網絡這樣的移動設備之應用實例，並允許設備上的網絡瀏覽器、電子郵件客戶端、地圖程式等經由[[Tor|Tor]]網絡之流量路由上為用戶提供匿名之需要的應用。<ref name="ehack">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ehacking.net/2011/04/orbot-tor-anonymous-on-android.html|accessdate=21 July 2012|publisher=[[eHacking.net|eHacking.net]]|title=Orbot: Tor- Anonymous On Android|first=Irfan|last=Shakeel|date=April 2011|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226125205/https://www.ehacking.net/2011/04/orbot-tor-anonymous-on-android.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

Orbot被用來保持在[[智能手机|智能手机]]上的通信安全而阻絕政府可能的監控，而實際上世界各地的政府經常監控不同政見者的手機通信。<ref>{{Cite web|accessdate=21 July 2012|title=From encryption to darknets: As governments snoop, activists fight back|first=Cyrus|publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|last=Farivar|date=15 February 2012|url=http://arstechnica.com/business/the-networked-society/2012/02/from-encryption-to-darknets-as-governments-snoop-activists-fight-back.ars|archive-date=2012-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503214051/http://arstechnica.com/business/the-networked-society/2012/02/from-encryption-to-darknets-as-governments-snoop-activists-fight-back.ars|dead-url=no}}</ref>

